{
  "stem": "214.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You just don't go into American officer, especially since you don't speak the language.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, when we told them who we are, they, maybe 15 minutes later, sent a delegation to the poor fellow that didn't know what they were talking about to remove us from the Polish barracks because they don't want to be together with Jews.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So we still couldn't travel, until, I don't know, about another week or two weeks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No, I think, no, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think Rabbi Eskin, then I think a couple of Jews came to our-- no.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Yeah, this was still in Weinsberg.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were some Italian boys who became our good friends.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were giving performances.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they knew that-- we told them that we are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they didn't have any objections to-- to that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were-- and then I think there were a couple of-- a few Jewish inmates started coming out and-- and still got into Weinsberg.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, [SIGHS] it was something, I know, that Marina and I, we were arrested by the Americans because we wanted to escape from this-- yeah, then they announced that we have to stay in this camp until, you know, they will dispose, one way or the other, with us.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we, because we still had our room in the TB sanatorium, and our things, so we decided, well, we are going to steal out, the two of us, Marina and I, and go.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then-- then we'll come back when things straighten out, whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we walked out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we started walking down the road.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And before we knew, a jeep came, picked us up, took us back to the camp, and closed us in.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
